      <bioghist id="aspace_0640a1928c9fac2924b089f56ea96564">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Richard Pryor (1940-2005), American stand-up comedian, social critic, and actor.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_3bfddae70af015523fdef98c8b01fd49">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains film scripts, promotional photographs taken on film sets, press kits, and a storyboard relating to the acting career of Richard Pryor. The collection spans 1971 to 1991.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_4d5817a690463b465ceb761f6ef99104">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is organized into four series: Scripts, Photographs, Press Kits, and Storyboard.</p>  
      </arrangement>
